premise_source_doc_sentence: In 2000 he recorded Dímelo , a new gold record , and in 2002 Gitano cubano , accompanied by Raimundo Amador , Lolita and Cuban singers Lucrecia and David Montes .
In 1999 he repeated the gold record with the soundtrack of the film Sobreviviré .
After a long silence , in which he only sang for the Evangelical Church , in 1998 he returned with the album Por tu ausencia , a live recording of greatest hits and new songs that was a gold record .
